News.Title: Barflex Polyfilms: Flat Debut on NSE SME, Rises 5% Post-Listing
News.Summary: Barflex Polyfilms shares listed at ₹60 on NSE SME, matching the IPO price. The stock later rallied to ₹63, a 5% increase. The ₹39.42 crore IPO was oversubscribed 151.52 times, with NIIs oversubscribing 373 times and retail 98.48 times. Proceeds will fund capital expenditure and general corporate purposes.
